<text top="1706" left="692" width="464" height="65" font="font13" id="p1_t9" reading_order_no="8" segment_no="2" tag_type="text">hether  we  are  aware  of  it </text>
<text top="1766" left="674" width="481" height="54" font="font14" id="p1_t10" reading_order_no="9" segment_no="2" tag_type="text">or  not,  knowledge  flows </text>
<text top="1812" left="654" width="501" height="62" font="font15" id="p1_t11" reading_order_no="10" segment_no="2" tag_type="text">within  human  society  and </text>
<text top="1863" left="638" width="518" height="63" font="font16" id="p1_t12" reading_order_no="11" segment_no="2" tag_type="text">in  the  Internet-mediated </text>
<text top="1918" left="620" width="305" height="61" font="font17" id="p1_t13" reading_order_no="12" segment_no="2" tag_type="text">interconnection </text>
